European Stock-Index Futures Erase Earlier Advance Before Rate Decisions

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-09-08T06:24:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/european-stock-index-futures-erase-earlier-advance-before-rate-decisions.html
European stock-index futures erased
gains before interest-rate decisions by the European Central
Bank and the Bank of England.  Euro Stoxx 50 futures contracts expiring this month climbed
less than 0.1 percent to 2,150 as of 7:22 a.m. in London. The
contracts had earlier risen as much as 0.4 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Adam Haigh at 
 ahaigh1@bloomberg.net  